#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:4
msgid "CMake"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:6
msgid ""
"For a thorough description of the module system see the :doc:`ModuleSystem` "
"section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:8
msgid "The CMake API can be separated into several categories:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:12
msgid "**Module APIs** |module|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:14
msgid ""
"This category includes functions to find and build VTK modules. A module is "
"a set of related functionality. These are then compiled together into "
"libraries at the \"kit\" level. Each module may be enabled or disabled "
"individually and its dependencies will be built as needed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:19
msgid ""
"All functions strictly check their arguments. Any unrecognized or invalid "
"values for a function cause errors to be raised."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:24
msgid "**Internal APIs** |module-internal|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:26
msgid ""
"The VTK module system provides some API functions for use by other code "
"which consumes VTK modules (primarily language wrappers). This file "
"documents these APIs. They may start with `_vtk_module`, but they are "
"intended for use in cases of language wrappers or dealing with trickier "
"third party packages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:33
msgid "**Implementation APIs** |module-impl|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:35
msgid ""
"These functions are purely internal implementation details. No guarantees "
"are made for them and they may change at any time (including wrapping code "
"calls). Note that these functions are usually very lax in their argument "
"parsing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:41
msgid "**Python Wrapping APIs** |module-wrapping-python|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:43
msgid "APIs for wrapping modules for Python."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:47
msgid "**Java Wrapping APIs** |module-wrapping-java|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:49
msgid "APIs for wrapping modules for Java."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:53
msgid "**JavaScript Wrapping APIs** |module-wrapping-javascript|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:55
msgid "APIs for wrapping modules for JavaScript."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:59
msgid "**Serialization APIs** |module-serialization|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:61
msgid "APIs for generation (de)serialization code for modules."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/cmake/cmake-modules.rst:65
msgid "**Support APIs**  |module-support|"
msgstr ""

